title: What did I say
lyrics:
Mwolaess-eo
Naega mwolaess-eo
Bunmyeong huhoehal geolago geuleoji anh-ass-eo
Babo gat-ass-eo neomu babo gat-ass-eo
Neoneun naleul geuleohge tteonabeolimyeon an dwaess-eo



Nuga naboda neoleul manh-i algess-eo

Nuga naboda neol deo salanghagess-eo

Nuga namankeum neoleul ihaehagess-eo

Nuga nunbichman bwado ne mam al su issgess-eo



Mwolaess-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Gyeolgug-en dasi naege ol geolago haji anh-ass-eo



Mwolaess-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Na gat-eun salam eobs-eul geolago haji anh-ass-eo



Geuleoge wae nal tteonass-eo geunal



Neuj-eoss-eo

Imi neuj-eoss-eo

Doedol-agagien neomu meolli wabeolyeoss-eo



Neon hangsang nae mal-eul deudji anh-ass-eo

Maeilgat-i maeilgat-i

Neon hangsang geulaeseo maemdol-ass-eoss-eo

Maeilgat-i maeilgat-i

Nan neoui nun-e

Geojis-eul boyeojun jeog-i eobsgo

Neon nae siyaui hwansang an-e

Bal-eul deul-yeoss-eoss-eo

Nan neoui boineun

Geu jache-ui jonjaeleul mid-eossgo

Neon geu dwieseo

Naege bulsin-eulo nam-aiss-eoss-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Ije amuleohji anh-a

Nega gyeolgug naege

Ol geolago haji anh-ass-eo?

Imi tteonass-eo neol bonaegi jeon-e

Nae ma-eum-i geogil imi

Tteona meolli geol-eowassneungeol



Mwolaess-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Gyeolgug-en dasi naege ol geolago haji anh-ass-eo



Mwolaess-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Na gat-eun salam eobs-eul geolago haji anh-ass-eo



Mwolaess-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Gyeolgug-en huhoehage doel geolago haji anh-ass-eo



Mwolaess-eo

Naega mwolaess-eo

Na gat-eun salam eobs-eul geolago haji anh-ass-eo



Mwo haess-eo

Geuttaeneun mwo haess-eo

Naega neol jab-eul ttae geuttae neon mwo haess-eo
